<main>
<div class="row">
  <div class="col l12 s12">
    <h4 class="??">{{ genre }}</h4>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="row">
  <div class="col s12">
    <p>Now that you've decided which direction our hero should go, use the space below to continue the adventure...</p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="row">
    <form class="col s12">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="input-field col s12">
          <textarea id="story" class="materialize-textarea" data-length="2000"></textarea>
        </div>
      </div>
    </form>
</div>

<div class="row">
  <div class="col s12">
    <p>Before you leave, create two choices for our hero to make. Choices could include which direction to go in, which door to go through, or which magic potion to drink...it's up to you! Make them good, though, because the next adventurer will continue the story from here!</p>
  </div>
<div class="row">
  <div class="col s5">
      <p>Choice 1:</p>
          <div class="input-field inline">
            <input id="choice1" type="text" class="validate" required>
          </div>
  </div>
  <div class="col s5 offset-2">
      <p>Choice 2:</p>
          <div class="input-field inline">
            <input id="choice2" type="text" class="validate" required>
          </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="row">
  <div class="col s12">
    <button class="btn" type="submit">Submit</button>
  </div>
</div>
</main>